attributes.long-description:
Explore the beginnings of the popular FINAL FANTASY® series. Now celebrating its 25th anniversary, FINAL FANTASY® has become one of the most well-known and beloved video game franchises of all time. Now, take a tour through the first two installments of this incredible series. Gather your party mates, level up, and help save the world in the original FINAL FANTASY®. Then, gear up again for a new fight, with new characters and new villains in FINAL FANTASY®II. Contains the full version of two classic games!

Download this PS one® Classic today!
